**APIFlowLens**  
**Description:**  
Monitors API behavior through a zoomed-in lens that highlights jitter, anomalies, and micro-bursts in performance.

```markdown
# APIFlowLens - High-Resolution API Analyzer

APIFlowLens focuses on fine-grained analysis of API responses, revealing subtle timing issues and response deviations.

## Features
- Micro-latency detection  
- Anomaly burst tracking  
- Export: JSON / CSV

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/APIFlowLens.git
cd APIFlowLens
python monitor.py
